name: CUSTOM GREETING CARD | Christmas season only
description:
Custom illustrated holiday cards featuring hand-drawn portraits and lettering.

This is the most sweet and impressive way to greet the Holiday season!
We offer a fully customized greeting card illustration with your family portrait and hand-lettering text.

Cards are size A6 ( 10,5x15cm ) when folded, blank inside.

How to order:

you place the order on our shop;
soon after receiving the order we'll get in touch with you and send you the contract with all the details to fill to make your greeting card design.
It will be asked to you to send pictures of your family via email and we'll proceed to draw the order.
In the next 48 hours after sending infos and pics you'll receive your design preview.
You send changes if needed and receive the updated version of your order.
Once you approve the final illustration, your order is sent to print and we cannot make any changes or revisions and will not be responsible for any errors. 
The order will be shipped out to you as soon as your printing is complete.

Timing: 10 days + 4 business days delivery

description:
We draw and realize beautiful and unique slip-in Photo albums completely personalised to help you treasure cherished memories like your wedding or your baby first year of life.

name: LETTERPRESS WEDDING stationery | custom item
description:
SHHH MY DARLING wedding collection stationery offers beautiful and customizable options that give your guests the feeling that they were made just for you. 

Printed on a range of cotton uncoated papers of your choice.

Papers we use:

Zerkall Bütten 450gms
neutral white
A soft and thoothy that come in an incredible natural white colour with a untouchable vein of pale pink. Very romantic and perfect for wedding stationery and goods.

GMUND cotton 310 - 600 - 900 gms
new grey, linen cream, gentleman blue
A super thick and tough acid free paper that comes in three different great nouances.
Recommended both for letterpress and screenprint products.

PESCIA liscia by Fabriano 280 gms
natural white
One of the most famous classic Italian papers by Fabriano since 1782.
A smooth cotton paper able to take a great bite from the letterpress. 

ARTURO by Magnani 600 gms
Arturo Fine Stationery is one of most popular line for letterpress and stationery. These mouldmade papers have a soft, luxurious feel made possible by Magnani's proprietary "corona" felt. 

Wide range of coloured envelopes to match with, depending on your needs and your palette.

Timing: drawing an order takes approximatively 2- 4 weeks, depending on client rush and the size of the order.
Printing and getting it ready takes up to one week.
We ship all orders with international couriers that deliver in 4 business days and provide tracking number.

What we offer at the moment is the following, here you can download our PDF so you have an idea of what we do:


Invitation + matching envelope starts from 3.00 EUR per guest.


If you are interested in wedding stationery from our catalog please take a look to our pdf here:
http://issuu.com/jennyschenal/docs
/wedding_catalog_updated

Once you know what pieces you’re interested in, please contact us and we’ll create a quote for you.

Shipping costs will be calculated depending on your order.
Standard and fast shipping options available.

Free colours and minimum changes.

Looking for fully customised stationery?
Contact us and ask for a quote! info@shhhmydarling.com

name: WEDDING STATIONERY
description:
We offer a range of standard wedding sets, both in digital printing and letterpress and, as you asked for, we do custom orders too.

Whether you'd like to go for a standard design, this will include adding your text and infos + free minimum changes, like adding or removing a detail or changing colurs.
If you'd like to change a lot - e.g. characters or background - then we consider it as a custom order, which costs a little more, due to hours of work  taken to realize a new illustration.
Maps are always custom, cause we draw them head to tail for each client.

We print all our orders on italian thick 320mg natural white uncoated paper.

A wide range of coloured envelopes to match with is available.
